# Edge-aligned square: each edge is exactly straight on the pen's trace, with
# corner curves of radius |pen_body| localized at each vertex (no bulges
# stretching across the polyline). Compare against `square_pen` which visits
# the same corners but lets the unavoidable arc dominate the inter-corner path.
line_to 30 0
line_to 30 30
line_to 0 30
line_to 0 0
